#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The freedb Submit tab sets up connection to a mail server or a web server "
#| "to submit new <acronym>CDDB</acronym> entries. This is useful if you do "
#| "not have your own system configured as a server."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Submit</guilabel> tab sets up connection to a mail server or a "
"web server to submit new <acronym>CDDB</acronym> entries. This is useful if "
"you do not have your own system configured as a server."
msgstr ""
"freedb-indsendelsesfanebladet indstiller forbindelsen til en e-mail-server "
"til at indsende nye <acronym>CDDB</acronym>-indgange. Dette er nyttigt hvis "
"du ikke har dit eget system indstillet som  en server. "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you plan to submit a CDDB entry, first you must decide between "
#| "submitting between &HTTP; and submitting the entry as an email (via "
#| "&SMTP;)."
msgid ""
"If you plan to submit a CDDB entry, enter your email address into the first "
"textbox."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du planlægger at indsende CDDB-information, skal du først bestemme om "
"du vil sende ind med &HTTP; eller send informationen ind som e-mail (via "
"&SMTP;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter a server name or port number in the text boxes provided. If "
"you want to send this information to the international servers, you do not "
"need to change anything."
msgstr ""
"Du kan indtaste et servernavn eller portnummer i tekstfelterne som der "
"bliver sørget for. Hvis du vil indsende informationen til de internationale "
"servere behøver du ikke ændre noget."

